item.dc:creator: @Project_Realm Project Realm

@Project_Realm wrote:

I posted on your other thread in Server Help, and the answer is the same. Changing a server from 317 all the way to 508 (almost 200 updates later) is very, very difficult. It’s not 100% impossible, but neither is building your own rocket ship and using it to get to Mars. So, it’s very unlikely you’ll be able to do it. Or the rocket ship thing.

Use my suggestion in the other post and you’re good to go.
